CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

July 5, 2006

[Cite as 07/05/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-3306.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2004-2122. State ex rel. White v. Preble Cty. Bd. of Commrs.

In Mandamus. On joint motion for approval of settlement agreement. It appearing to the court that the parties have entered into a settlement agreement resolving this cause, this cause is dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resniok, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur. Pfeifer and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., would grant the joint motion.
